{
  "texts": [
    "An updated version of the HCR dataset has been presented by Ioannidis et al. (2020).",
    "Rodríguez-Navarroa and Brito (2021) compared HCRs data on the national level based on the definition by Clarivate and Ioannidis and co-authors (Ioannidis et al., 2019 (Ioannidis et al.,, 2020)).",
    "Although the authors found a high correlation between the number of HCRs based on both definitions, they also found notable differences for countries with only a few numbers of HCRs.",
    "Rodríguez-Navarroa and Brito (2021) concluded that their empirical results validated the definitions of HCRs by Ioannidis and co-authors, and that \"the number of WoS [Web of Science]-HCR [by Clarivate] fails to assess correctly the success of research in some specific countries\".",
    "Given the criticism of Clarivate's HCRs approach, the aim of the following analyses is not to suggest an optimized approach."
  ]
}